Follow creatives to see their work in your feed.

You'll see their projects as they update and publish them, as well as all the work they appreciate, so you can see what's inspiring them.

Appreciate Projects You Like

When you appreciate a project, we handpick similar projects for you that you may also like. It also gives the project more exposure, as your followers will see the work you appreciate in their home feeds.

Also, its just a nice thing to do :)
